chunk_content: If the individual is self- identified as living with HIV, then HTS provision will not be a required element of this indicator. P Conducting risk assessments or screening to determine the need for HIV testing also meets the HTS R E component of PP_PREV. For example, if there is a ten-year-old girl enrolled in DREAMS, we would V anticipate that she would not need to be tested for HIV if a risk assessment determines that she is not E sexually active and she does not have any additional risk factors for HIV.
